"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"accessibility_concerns","title":"Accessibility concerns","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques#landmark_roles\">Landmark roles</a> are intended to be used sparingly, to identify larger overall sections of the document. Using too many landmark roles can create \"noise\" in screen readers, making it difficult to understand the overall layout of the page.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Will be part of WAI-ARIA 1.3, which is still being drafted.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Annotations\">ARIA annotations</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Accessibility concerns","id":"accessibility_concerns"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The comment landmark role semantically denotes a comment/reaction to some content on the page, or to a previous comment.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-09-13T12:22:39.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/accessibility/aria/roles/comment_role","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/accessibility/aria/roles/comment_role/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/7d2071f78f38f8be38